name: Governor Phil Scott

name: Governor Phil Scott
tweet: Today I announced twenty-four outdoor recreation community grants across the state. Vermont’s natural beauty, combined with outdoor recreation opportunities, are economic engines for our state and a driving force for why people visit and live in Vermont. 1/

name: Governor Phil Scott
tweet: Vermonters have been clear: we need more affordable housing. We have funding available to help make a transformative change to Vermont’s housing stock, but we need the legislature to act now so we can start moving this work forward.  Learn More:  https://t.co/nWy5m7iFtS
